  <interlinear-text guid="01eaa864-422a-4cb8-ad66-f0e76cfc4c95">
    <item type="title" lang="btz">1 - Si Layakh 8.2</item>
    <item type="source" lang="en">https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html</item>
    <item type="comment" lang="en">This appears to be a translation of part of the story from https://kaisosogarcia.blogspot.com/2016/04/si-layakh-cerita-rakyat-dari-kutacane.html. However, I have been told the Alas is good in it.</item>
    <item type="date-created" lang="en">2026-05-13 18:08:14.757</item>
    <item type="date-modified" lang="en">2026-05-14 13:59:13.967</item>
